节奏游戏，或称节奏动作游戏<ref>(2007-06-30). [http://uk.playstation.com/games-media/news/articles/detail/item75867/Rhythm-action-games-on-PlayStation/ "Rhythm action games on PlayStation"]. PlayStation.com. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref><ref>Alexander, Leigh (2008-03-02). [http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=18037 "EA Announces DS Rhythm Action Exclusive Zubo"]. [[GamaSutra|GamaSutra]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>，是一类挑战玩家节奏感的[[动作游戏|动作游戏]]<ref name="fundamentals" />。像《[[舞蹈革命|舞蹈革命]]》这类舞蹈游戏，或是《[[大金刚鼓|大金刚鼓]]》和《[[吉他英雄|吉他英雄]]》等音乐游戏，都属于节奏游戏。在一般的节奏游戏中，玩家需要按屏幕指示按键，按键和节拍同步、正确精准，就会得分<ref name="fundamentals" />。还有测试玩家歌唱能力的节奏游戏，会测量玩家的节奏和音高<ref name="krev" /><ref>Frushtick, Russ. [https://web.archive.org/web/20110615211806/http://www.ugo.com/ugo/html/article/?id=18042 "Rock Band Review"]. [[UGO|UGO]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>；亦有节奏游戏，要求玩家用不同按键力度，发出不同的音量<ref name="madmaestro">Smith, David (2002-04-14). [http://ps2.ign.com/articles/355/355561p1.html "Mad Maestro"]. [[IGN|IGN]]. Retrieved 2009-04-04.</ref>。玩家虽可即兴演奏歌曲<ref>Brudvig, Erik (2007-08-22). [http://ps2.ign.com/articles/814/814842p1.html "GC 2007: Guitar Hero III Progress Report"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071112120941/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/814/814842p1.html |date=2007-11-12 }}. [[IGN|IGN]]. Retrieved 1009-04-03.</ref>，但常会反复练习，来挑战高难度的歌曲和设定<ref>Cowan, Danny (2006-11-08). [http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=11610 "Critical Reception: RedOctane's/Harmonix's Guitar Hero II"]. [[GamaSutra|GamaSutra]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。某些节奏游戏挑战和[[Simon_says|Simon says]]类似，玩家需要观看，记忆并重复复杂的按键序列<ref>Shoemaker, Brad (2003-12-05). [http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/puzzle/spacechannel5specialedition/review.html "Space Channel 5 Special Edition Review"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208114816/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/puzzle/spacechannel5specialedition/review.html |date=2009-02-08 }}. [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。节奏游戏也可做成[[小游戏|小游戏]]，插入其他类型游戏中，或随其它小游戏捆绑为合集<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/rhythm-paradise-review | publisher = [[EuroGamer|EuroGamer]] | date =2009-05-05 | accessdate = 2011-11-16 | title = Rhythm Paradise Review | first = Simon | last = Parkin }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamesradar.com/tgs-2011-rhythm-thief-emperors-treasure-hands-preview/ | publisher = [[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] | date =2011-09-19 | accessdate = 2011-11-16 | title = TGS 2011: Rhythm Thief & the Emperor's Treasure hands-on preview | first = Henry | last = Gilbert }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-08-30-sega-confirms-rhythm-thief-for-3ds | publisher = [[EuroGamer|EuroGamer]] | date =2011-08-30 | accessdate = 2011-11-16 | title = Sega confirms Rhythm Thief for 3DS | first = Fred | last = Dutton }}</ref>。

部分节奏游戏画面中，会显示演奏者的角色化身，其会随玩家的输入而反应<ref name="fundamentals" />。然而节奏游戏的画面多为背景，演奏者化身亦主要供观众来观看<ref name="madmaestro" /><ref name="krev">Gerstmann, Jeff (2003-11-10). [http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/puzzle/karaokerevolution/review.html "Karaoke Revolution Review] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204235934/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/puzzle/karaokerevolution/review.html |date=2009-02-04 }}". [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。在单人模式中，玩家要和电脑控制的对手对战；在多人模式中，两名玩家化身可以正面竞争<ref name="fundamentals" />。随着节奏游戏的普及，特殊输入设备也有了市场<ref name="fundamentals">Rollings & Adams, p. 442</ref>，如仿吉他、鼓、沙球等乐器的控制器<ref name="edge">{{cite web |author=Graft, Kris |url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/there-was-guitar-hero |title=Before There Was Guitar Hero... – Edge Magazine |publisher=Next-gen.biz |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2011-09-08 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130115052003/http://www.next-gen.biz/features/there-was-guitar-hero |archive-date=2013-01-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。舞蹈游戏所用的压敏跳舞毯，则可让玩家在其上跳舞<ref name="ashcraft523" />。不过对于手柄等传统输入设备，大多节奏游戏依然支持<ref name="vib10" />。

== 历史 ==

节奏游戏的本源可追溯到电动游戏《西蒙》<ref name="edge" /><ref>Ashcraft, p. 55</ref>，这款游戏由[[拉尔夫·贝尔|拉尔夫·贝尔]]（[[米罗华奥德赛|米罗华奥德赛]]创造者）和[[霍华德·莫里森|霍华德·莫里森]]在1978年开发。《西蒙》创造了“呼应”机制，这种按键指令序列逐渐复杂，玩家不断重复的机制，后来由节奏游戏使用<ref name="edge" />。

=== 日本 ===

在[[Human_Entertainment|Human Entertainment]] 1987年发行的《[[Dance_Aerobics|舞蹈健美操]]》中，玩家可在任天堂[[红白机|红白机]]的外设[[Power_Pad|动力垫]]上，跳舞来创造音乐。据信，最早的真正节奏游戏是1996年的《[[啪啦啪啦啪|啪啦啪啦啪]]》<ref name="gamespotparappa">Kasavin, Greg (2006-01-28). [http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-2.html "The GameSpot Top 10 Rhythm Games: PaRappa the Rapper"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010160614/http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-2.html |date=2012-10-10 }}. [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>，这也是最早几款通常意义音乐游戏之一<ref>Ashcraft, p. 52</ref>。玩家游戏时需依屏幕指示按键，这一基本机制成为之后节奏游戏的核心。《啪嗒啪嗒啪》的成功开启音乐游戏市场的大门<ref name="edge" /><ref name="roots">Webster, Andrew (2008). [http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2009/03/ne-music-game-feature.ars "Roots of rhythm: a brief history of the music game genre"]. [[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]. Retrieved 2011-10-13.</ref>。1997年，[[科乐美|科乐美]]在日本[[街机|街机]]推出DJ主题节奏游戏《[[狂热节拍|狂热节拍]]》（Beatmania），游戏[[街机基板|街机基板]]采用音乐键盘式按键，同时基板上还有仿黑胶唱片的橡胶垫<ref name="ashcraft54">Ashcraft, p. 54</ref>。科乐美在《狂热节拍》意外大热后，将其游戏与音乐部门改名Bemani，该名称有向游戏致敬之意<ref name="ashcraft54" />。Bemani开始尝试其他的节奏游戏<ref name="ashcraft56">Ashcraft, p. 56</ref>，其成功作有《吉他高手》和1998年的《[[Pop'n_Music|流行音乐]]》，前者使用吉他形游戏控制器，后者和《狂热节拍》类似，要求玩家按色彩各异的按键<ref name="ashcraft56" /><ref>Ashcraft, p. 58</ref>。吉他高手系列虽继续随日本新街机推行，但在海外市场影响力不大，Red Octane和Harmonix在2005年，发行了西方口味的类似游戏《吉他英雄》<ref name="edge" />。一般而言，因外设制作成本高昂，加上零售价格随之增长，日本街机节奏游戏很少出口海外<ref name="roots" />。Bemani在1999年推出的《[[狂热鼓手|狂热鼓手]]》采用鼓包控制器，游戏可和《吉他高手》联动，模仿即兴演奏。后来Harmonix也将该理念用在《摇滚乐队》上<ref name="edge" />。

在1998年节奏游戏《[[舞蹈革命|舞蹈革命]]》中，玩家需依屏幕所示指令，在压敏舞垫上跳舞<ref name="ashcraft523">Ashcraft, pp. 52–53</ref>。游戏和《吉他高手》、《狂热鼓手》与《狂热节拍》不同，在日本内外都获高度成功（不过《狂热节拍》在欧洲有所成功）<ref>Ashcraft, p. 57</ref>。[[艾尼克斯|艾尼克斯]]同年发行了《[[Bust_a_Groove|纵情跳跃]]》，这款游戏同样为舞蹈游戏，但采用较传统的输入方式。游戏支持一对一竞争模式，且比典型节奏游戏更为自由<ref name="edge" /><ref>Gouskos, Carrie (2006-01-28). [http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-8.html "The GameSpot Top 10 Rhythm Games: Bust a Groove"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090622132425/http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-8.html |date=2009-06-22 }}. [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。

《啪嗒啪嗒啪》制作方[[七音社|七音社]]在1999年发行了《[[Vib-Ribbon|Vib-Ribbon]]》。游戏并非用乐器形控制器，而是要求玩家在合适时机按键，让主角穿过障碍训练场。游戏关卡由背景音乐生成，玩家可以调换所插音频CD。游戏虽以其独特风格和艺术性获得好评，但简单的[[矢量图形|矢量图形]]证明其难有市场，游戏最终未在北美发行<ref name="edge" /><ref name="vib10">Calvert, Justin (2006-01-28). [http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-6.html "The GameSpot Top 10 Rhythm Games: Vib-Ribbon"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010160123/http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-6.html |date=2012-10-10 }}. [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。[[世嘉|世嘉]]于1999年和2000年，分别在街机和[[Dreamcast|Dreamcast]]推出《[[Amigo的桑巴|Amigo的桑巴]]》，游戏采用沙球形动作感应控制器。游戏支持双人模式，可以向观众展示，并支持玩家游戏时社交<ref name="edge" /><ref>Gerstmann, Jeff (2006-01-28). [http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-3.html "The GameSpot Top 10 Rhythm Games: Samba de Amigo"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010160809/http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-3.html |date=2012-10-10 }}. [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。《[[太鼓达人|太鼓达人]]》于2000年发行，游戏将日本传统乐器[[太鼓|太鼓]]与现代流行乐相结合，在日本街机市场大获成功<ref>Ashcraft, pp. 59–60</ref>。游戏后以“Taiko Drum Master”名义在西方主机发行，系列也在日本继续发行新作<ref name="edge" />。2001年，吉他手主角游戏《[[Gitaroo_Man|吉他小子]]》发行，和4年后采用吉他形控制器的《[[吉他英雄|吉他英雄]]》不同，《吉他小子》采用传统的控制器<ref name="edge" />。《吉他小子》创作人矢野庆一之后创作了《[[押忍！战斗！应援团|押忍！战斗！应援团]]》，这款[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]节奏游戏使用了掌机的触摸屏功能。应西方大量呼声，改版《[[精英节拍特工|精英节拍特工]]》在西方发行；此外日本有[[燃燒！熱血韻律魂_押忍！戰鬥！應援團2|一款续作]]<ref>Kohler, Chris (2006-09-16). [http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=0&cId=3153670 "Cheer Squad: Why iNiS Wants to Make You Happier"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604232712/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=0&cId=3153670 |date=2011-06-04 }}. [[1UP.com|1UP.com]]. Retrieved 2009-04-14.</ref>。

=== 北美 ===

[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]的一个电脑音乐社团在1995年建立了Harmonix，公司受《啪嗒啪嗒啪》的启发，从1998年起开发音乐游戏<ref>[[Alex_Rigopulos|Rigopulos, Alex]], in Steinberg, p. 6</ref>。公司在2001年发行了《Frequency》，玩家在游戏中可以控制多条乐轨。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的莱安·戴维斯写道，和早期节奏游戏相比，该作的创作自由感更强<ref>Davis, Ryan (2006-01-28). [http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-9.html "The GameSpot Top 10 Rhythm Games: Frequency"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010160915/http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-9.html |date=2012-10-10 }}. [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。《Frequency》获得媒体的叫好声，但不能直观呈现演奏效果的抽象风格却不叫座<ref name="edge" />。Harmonix在2003年发行了仿《Frequency》风格的续作《Amplitude》<ref>(2003-01-08). [http://uk.gamespot.com/ps2/puzzle/amplitude/news.html?sid=2908221&mode=news "Sony announces Amplitude"] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120715075000/http://uk.gamespot.com/ps2/puzzle/amplitude/news.html?sid=2908221&mode=news |date=2012-07-15 }}. [[Gamespot|Gamespot]]. Retrieved 2010-07-05.</ref>。此后公司发行的游戏更注重社交性，如[[卡拉OK|卡拉OK]]主题游戏《[[卡拉OK革命|卡拉OK革命]]》（2003）和《[[歌唱之星|歌唱之星]]》（2004）<ref name="edge" />。[[南梦宫|南梦宫]]开发的[[GameCube|GameCube]]游戏《[[大金刚鼓|大金刚鼓]]》在2003年发行，这款借任天堂[[大金刚系列|大金刚]]品牌的游戏获得广泛成功<ref name="edge" />。

==== 外设式游戏 ====

2005年，Harmonix和小型发行商[[RedOctane|RedOctane]]发行了《吉他英雄》。该游戏从Bemani的《吉他高手》中汲取灵感，但采用西方摇滚乐。因《舞蹈革命》的大量续作和效仿作品，节奏游戏停滞不前，《吉他英雄》的出现让其重新恢复活力<ref>Navarro, Alex (2006-01-28). [http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-10.html "The GameSpot Top 10 Rhythm Games: Dance Dance Revolution"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010161003/http://uk.gamespot.com/features/6142896/p-10.html |date=2012-10-10 }}. [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref><ref>2008. [http://www.ugo.com/games/best-of-e3/?cur=Best-Rhythm-Game-Rock-Band-2 "Best Rhythm Game: Rock Band 2"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915090625/http://www.ugo.com/games/best-of-e3/?cur=Best-Rhythm-Game-Rock-Band-2 |date=2008-09-15 }}. [[UGO|UGO]]. Retrieved 2009-04-29.</ref>。《吉他英雄》有多部续作，系列总收入超过10亿美元，系列第三作是北美2007年最畅销的游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/news/guitar-hero-breaks-1-bln |title=Guitar Hero Breaks $1 bln – Edge Magazine |publisher=Next-gen.biz |date=2008-01-21 |accessdate=2011-09-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150802013106/http://www.next-gen.biz/news/guitar-hero-breaks-1-bln/ |archivedate=2015-08-02 }}</ref>。Harmonix在吉他英雄后又推出[[摇滚乐队系列|摇滚乐队系列]]，该系列也赚得1亿美元。摇滚乐队作品支持多乐器控制器和多人合作模式，玩家可以扮演整支乐队<ref name="fox">2009-03-26. [http://investor.ea.com/releasedetail.cfm?releaseid=373278 "Rock Band(R) Franchise Officially Surpasses $1 Billion in North American Retail Sales, According to the NPD Group(1)"]. [[Fox_Business_Network|Fox Business]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。吉他英雄系列之后的作品，[[Neversoft|Neversoft]]开发的《吉他英雄 世界巡演》也采用乐队导向<ref>Thomas, Aaron (2008-11-11). [http://uk.gamespot.com/xbox360/puzzle/guitarheroiv/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review "Guitar Hero World Tour Review"]{{dead link|date=六月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}. [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。吉他英雄也有作品改编自某些乐队，如[[金属乐队|金属乐队]]和[[空中铁匠|空中铁匠]]<ref name="bbc">Cochrane, Greg (2008-12-16). [http://news.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/hi/music/newsid_7785000/7785158.stm "Rock bands turn to Guitar Hero"]. BBC ''[[Newsbeat|Newsbeat]]''. Retrieved 2009-04-03.</ref>。玩家可从网上，购买吉他英雄和摇滚乐队的追加歌曲，这成为公司又一道收入来源；游戏收录音乐的艺术家会获得使用费，其名气亦随之提升，随之带动其音乐销量<ref name="fox" /><ref name="bbc" />。吉他英雄和摇滚乐队拓宽了主机游戏市场及其消费群体，游戏人气带动提升了游戏机销量<ref name="overtakessports">{{cite web |author=Crossley, Rob |url=http://www.next-gen.biz/news/music-overtakes-sports-genre |title=Music Overtakes Sports Genre – Edge Magazine |publisher=Next-gen.biz |date=2008-10-21 |accessdate=2011-09-08 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130115113001/http://www.next-gen.biz/news/music-overtakes-sports-genre |archive-date=2013-01-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。据报道，音乐游戏是北美在2008年第二流行电子游戏类型（仅次于动作），53%玩家为女性<ref name="overtakessports" />。音乐游戏在2008年的最高点，占据电子游戏市场份额的18%<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-02-18/new-rock-band-game-said-to-be-developed-for-latest-consoles | title = New Rock Band Game Said to Be Developed for Latest Consoles | first = Danielle | last = Burger | publisher = [[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg]] | date = 2015-02-19 | accessdate = 2015-02-19 }}</ref>。

电子游戏业分析称，2009年是节奏游戏的危急年，这将可以衡量此类游戏未来的成功<ref name="independent gh influence">{{cite news | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/rocktastic-how-guitar-hero-brought-stardom-to-the-masses-1669257.html | title = Rocktastic: How Guitar Hero brought stardom to the masses | publisher = ''[[The_Independent|The Independent]]'' | date = 2009-04-16 | accessdate = 2009-04-16 | location=}}</ref>。《吉他英雄》和《摇滚乐队》系列都有发展，它们进入了掌上游戏设备和手机市场。亦有面向特定流派和人口的游戏面世，如采用流行乐的《[[乐队英雄|乐队英雄]]》和面向年轻玩家的《[[乐高摇滚乐队|乐高摇滚乐队]]》。因乐器控制器销量减少，游戏音乐销量在上半年下降；媒体推测，玩家已经购买此类控制器，并重新将之使用<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=24482 | title = Analysis: Guitar Hero/Rock Band Retail Sales Down By Half | first = Matt | last = Matthews | date = 2009-07-21 | accessdate = 2009-07-22 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] }}</ref>。分析预测，《[[吉他英雄5|吉他英雄5]]》和《[[披头士：摇滚乐队|披头士：摇滚乐队]]》美版首月销量皆将达100万上下<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.gamespot.com/news/6232261.html|title=Beatles: Rock Band outsold Guitar Hero 5 – Analysts|first=Brendan|last=Sinclair|date= 2009-10-08|accessdate=2009-10-08|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]}}</ref>，但实际销量仅约预测的一半<ref name="npd sales">{{cite news | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2009/10/beatles-rock-band-sales.html | title = The Beatles: Rock Band debuts to solid but not stellar sales | work = [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | first = Ben | last = Fritz | date = 2009-10-19 | accessdate = 2009-10-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=25739 | title = Analysis: Guitar Hero Vs. Rock Band – Behind The Numbers | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | first = Matt | last = Matthews | date = 2009-10-23 | accessdate = 2009-10-23 }}</ref>。游戏销量未达预期，部分因为2000年代后半，电子游戏业的衰退；Harmonix CEO亚历克斯·里格珀利斯当时认为，吉他英雄和摇滚乐队是当时市场最贵的电子游戏<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2014-05-19-rigopulos-dont-blame-activision-for-rhythm-bubble-burst | title = Rigopulos: Don't blame Activision for rhythm bubble burst | first = Brendan | last = Sinclair | date =2014-05-19 | accessdate = 2014-05-19 | publisher = [[GameIndustry.biz|GameIndustry.biz]] }}</ref>。分析还称此标志市场饱和<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=25712 | title = Analyst: Mixed September NPD Means More Choppy Waters Ahead For Industry | publisher =[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | first= Leigh | last = Alexander | date = 2009-10-20 | accessdate =2009-10-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/89407-Guitar-Hero-Gets-Greatest-Hits | title = Guitar Hero Gets 'Greatest Hits' | first = Logan | last = Fredrick | date = 2009-02-12 | accessdate = 2009-02-16 | publisher = [[The_Escapist_(magazine)|the escapist]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=208086 | title = Activision has three new IPs for 2009 | date = 2009-02-12 | accessdate = 2009-02-16 | publisher = ''[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]''}}</ref>。此外节奏游戏停滞不前，系列不断重复基本玩法，让消费者无意购买新作<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2009/11/music-game-sales/ | title = Music Games Aren't Dead, Just Waiting to Be Reborn | first = Chris | last = Kohler | date = 2009-11-16 | accessdate = 2009-11-17 | work = [[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] }}</ref>。亚历克斯认为，摇滚乐队和吉他英雄间，市场只能存其一的激烈品牌信仰之争，进一步让游戏走向衰退<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.theage.com.au/digital-life/games/blogs/screenplay/pop-goes-the-music-games-20120618-20k7b.html | title = Pop goes the music games | work = [[The_Age|The Age]] | first = Jason | last = Hill | date = 2012-06-19 | accessdate = 2012-06-19 }}</ref>。因此，分析下调了对音乐游戏的未来期望，如吉他英雄“衍生作品”《DJ英雄》美版第一季度的销量预测，从160万降低至60万<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/dj-hero-demand-well-below-expectations | title = DJ Hero demand 'well below' expectations | publisher = [[Eurogamer#GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]] | date = 2009-10-26 | accessdate = 2009-10-26 | first = Matt | last = Martin }}</ref>。节奏游戏的销售额从2008年的14.7亿美元，降至2009年的7亿美元。分析预测，市场会稳定在“健康的”5－6亿美元，即[[決勝時刻系列|決勝時刻系列]]的水平<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/12/18/us-2009-games-idUSTRE5BH5DS20091218 | title = Sales Of Music Video Games Plummet In 2009 | publisher = Reuters | date =2009-12-18 |accessdate = 2011-10-24 | first = Antony | last =Bruno}}</ref>。[[威布证券|威布证券]]分析师米迦勒·帕切特推测，随着节奏游戏市场饱和，其产业占有量将从1/3降低到2009年的12%<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/content_display/industry/news/e3i793156d6041aecbf8cda2e2be5defbc9 | title = Analyst: Music Genre Dragging Down Videogame Sales | first = Antony | last= Bruno | date = 2010-01-11 | accessdate = 2010-10-24 | work = [[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] }}</ref>。

节奏游戏市场的疲软，影响了游戏开发商、发行商和销售商。后两类公司确信，大多消费者在2010年时，至少已有一套乐器控制器，故提升了将软件和下载内容销售的地位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/213777/music-games-need-to-refocus-not-reboot/ |title=Music games need to refocus, not reboot |publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]] |date=2010-01-29 |accessdate=2010-02-18 |first=Joe |last=Rybicki |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100204132115/http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/213777/music-games-need-to-refocus-not-reboot/ |archivedate=2010-02-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[动视|动视]]将2010年吉他英雄的销售计划缩减，只销售两款游戏，将[[最小存货单位|最小存货单位]]从2009年的25下调至2010年的10<ref name="vg247 2010 skus">{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2010/02/10/actibliz-full-year-financials-2009-60-million-guitar-hero-songs-download/ | title = Acti Bliz slashes music SKUs, 60 million Guitar Hero songs downloaded | first = Stephany | last = Nunneley | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | date = 2010-02-10 | accessdate = 2010-02-10 }}</ref>。动视将数家内部工作室关闭，其中有RedOctane、Neversoft的吉他英雄部门，以及[[Underground_Development|Underground Development]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3177918 |title=Activision Confirms Studio Layoffs |first=Steve |last=Watts |date=2010-02-11 |accessdate=2010-02-11 |publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120716173245/http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3177918 |archivedate=2012-07-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/6250760.html |title=RedOctane closed by Activision? |first=Brian |last=Sinclair |date=2010-02-12 |accessdate=2010-02-12 |publisher=[[Gamespot|Gamespot]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100215172222/http://www.gamespot.com/news/6250760.html |archivedate=2010-02-15 }}</ref>。[[维亚康姆|维亚康姆]]在2007年《摇滚乐队》成功后，向Harmonix投资1.5亿美元，在2009年销售疲软后，维亚康姆征求“大量”撤回投资<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/27220/Viacom_To_Seek_Substantial_Refund_On_Harmonix_Rock_Band_Bonus_Dollars.php | title = Viacom To Seek 'Substantial' Refund On Harmonix Rock Band Bonus Dollars | first = Leigh | last = Alexander | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2010-02-12 | accessdate = 2010-02-18 }}</ref>。维亚康姆还和音乐版权管理公司磋商，调低摇滚乐队系列的音乐授权费<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/content_display/industry/e3ib5173b54f64bf8d208b13bce1a54d2cf | title = Viacom CEO: We Need To Pay Less For Music In Videogames | first = Glenn | last = Peoples | date = 2010-02-12 | accessdate = 2010-02-18 | work = [[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] }}</ref>。维亚康姆最终在2010年第三季度，开始寻求Harmonix买主<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/31569/Viacom_Searching_For_Buyer_That_Will_Be_Better_Fit_For_Harmonix.php | title = Viacom Searching For Buyer That Will Be 'Better Fit' For Harmonix | first = Kris | last = Graft | date= 2010-11-16 | accessdate= 2010-11-16 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] }}</ref>。节奏游戏开发商在2010年，开始在产品中加入新功能。比如《[[摇滚乐队3|摇滚乐队3]]》和《[[激情演奏：六弦飞舞|激情演奏：六弦飞舞]]》使用带弦的吉他控制器，并皆有教程模块，指导玩家精确指法<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/199467/fear_and_loathing_at_e3_awards_and_accolades.html | title = Fear and Loathing at E3: Awards and Accolades | first = Chris | last = Holt | date = 2010-06-21 | accessdate = 2010-06-21 | work = [[MacWorld|MacWorld]] }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/17386/119145 | title = Next-Gen Music Video Games: Real Instruments, Motion-Sensing | work = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | date = 2010-06-21 | accessdate = 2010-06-21 | first = Scott | last = Steinberg }}</ref>。然而新内容未能挽回2010年音乐游戏的颓势。《[[吉他英雄：摇滚战士|吉他英雄：摇滚战士]]》与《[[DJ英雄2|DJ英雄2]]》美版首周销量分别为8.6万和5.9万<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=269873 | title = Guitar Hero: Warriors of Rock makes 'fairly dreadful start' | first = Tom | last = Ivan | publisher = [[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]] | date = 2010-10-15 | accessdate = 2010-10-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2010-11-17-tony-hawk-shred-flops-with-only-3000-units-sold-in-us | title= Tony Hawk: Shred flops with only 3000 units sold in US | first = Matt | last = Martin | date= 2010-11-17 | accessdate= 2010-11-17 | publisher = GamesIndustry.biz }}</ref>，而2008年的《吉他英雄III》首周114万，销量反差强烈<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/news/guitar-hero-warriors-rock-sales-disappoint |title=Analyst: Guitar Hero: Warriors of Rock Sales Disappoint in September |first=Dustin |last=Quillen |date=2010-10-13 |accessdate=2010-10-15 |publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/694aKCcFS?url=http://www.1up.com/news/guitar-hero-warriors-rock-sales-disappoint |archivedate=2012-07-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/3854/npd_behind_the_numbers_october_.php | title = NPD: Behind The Numbers, October 2008 | first = Matt | last= Matthews | date = 2008-11-17 | accessdate= 2010-11-19 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] }}</ref>。到2010年10月，音乐游戏净销售额越2亿美元，为2008年同期的1/5。分析称节奏游戏到年底时，收益难破4亿美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6210/npd_behind_the_numbers_october_.php | title = NPD: Behind the Numbers, October 2010 | first = Matt | last = Matthews | date =2010-11-19 | accessdate= 2010-11-19 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] }}</ref>；后统计年底销售额不到3亿美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/blogs/gear-up/guitar-hero-not-dead-says-game-maker-activision-20110418 | title = 'Guitar Hero' Not Dead, Says Game Maker Activision | work = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | date = 2011-04-18 | accessdate = 2011-04-18 | first = Scott | last = Steinberg }}</ref>。

到2010年底，媒体认为节奏游戏“确实走过了全盛期”，开发商将注意力转向下载内容和潜在的体感集成系统<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/31641/Analysis_US_Music_Game_Sales_Have_Dropped_Fivefold_Annually_Since_2008.php | title = Analysis: U.S. Music Game Sales Have Dropped Fivefold Annually Since 2008 | date = 2010-11-19 | accessdate= 2010-11-19 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] }}</ref>。維亞康姆在2010年下半年，将Harmonix卖给一间投资回报集团，允许其继续开发摇滚乐队和[[舞蹈中心|舞蹈中心]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2010/11/viacom-sells-harmonix/ | title = Harmonix Sale Signals Meltdown of 'Plastic Instrument' Biz (Update) | first = Chris | last = Kohler | date= 2010-11-11 | accessdate = 2011-02-09 | work =[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] }}</ref>。动视以节奏游戏不景气为由，在2011年2月关闭了吉他英雄部门<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/32946/Activision_Dissolves_Guitar_Hero_Business_Refocuses_On_Digital.php | title = Activision Dissolves Guitar Hero Business, Refocuses On Digital | first = Leigh | last = Alexander | date = 2011-02-09 | accessdate = 2011-02-09 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] }}</ref>。有分析称，外设节奏游戏接下来三五年依旧不景气，之后因数字销售模式或新游戏机面世，销量会重新起来<ref>{{cite web | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/02/analysis-will-players-see-a-guitar-hero-encore/1 | title = Analysis: The end of an era for 'Guitar Hero' | work = [[USA_Today|USA Today]] | date = 2011-02-10 | accessdate = 2011-02-12 | first = Mike | last = Snider | first2 = Brett | last2 = Molina }}</ref><ref name="mcv no heroes">{{cite web | url = http://www.mcvuk.com/features/863/No-More-Guitar-Heroes | title = No More (Guitar) Heroes | publisher = [[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|MCV]] | date = 2011-02-18 | accessdate = 2011-02-18 | first = Christopher | last = Dring }}</ref>。但Harmonix宣布，公司在2013年转向新游戏，摇滚乐队下载内容更新停止，标志了外设式音乐游戏时代走向终结<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2013/04/02/quot-american-pie-quot-closes-out-rock-band-39-s-dlc.aspx | title = [Updated] "American Pie" Closes Out Rock Band's DLC | first = Jeff | last = Cork | date = 2013-04-02 | accessdate = 2013-04-05 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] }}</ref>。

==== 未来方向 ====

随着2010年，Xbox 360和PlayStation 3相继引入运动控制器[[Kinect|Kinect]]和[[PlayStation_Move|PlayStation Move]]，一些分析称，使用平台无关控制器的舞蹈与乐队式游戏，会振兴节奏游戏市场<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE62S08Z20100329 | title = Music video games primed for new dance revolution | work = [[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] | first = Antony | last= Bruno | date =2010-03-28 | accessdate = 2010-03-29 }}</ref>。《[[舞力全开_(游戏)|舞力全开]]》、《[[舞蹈中心|舞蹈中心]]》和《[[迈克尔·杰克逊：游戏|迈克尔·杰克逊：游戏]]》等舞蹈游戏采用了新体感技术。业界评论认为，外设式音乐游戏销量迟滞，加之流行音乐人气激增，舞蹈式游戏将持续繁荣发展<ref name="mcv no heroes" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/gamesblog/2011/feb/10/guitar-hero-axed | title = Guitar Hero axed: five reasons why music games are dying | work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date = 2011-02-10 | accessdate = 2011-02-10 | first= Keith | last = Stuart }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-20031267-1.html | title = Reason to fret: Guitar Hero is no more | first = Matt | last = Hickly | date = 2011-02-09 | accessdate = 2011-02-10 | publisher = [[CNET|CNET]] }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2011/02/10/ap/tech/main7338362.shtml | title = Party over for 'Guitar Hero,' but not music games | date = 2011-02-10 | accessdate = 2011-02-10 | agency = Associated Press }}</ref>。《舞力全开》和《舞蹈中心》在2010年下半年，推动了节奏游戏的销量；后者是北美2010年11月最畅销的Kinect游戏。按[[NPD集团|NPD集团]]统计，在两款游戏的推动下，节奏游戏销量比2009年11月高出38%<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.mcvuk.com/news/42181/NPD-Dance-games-spark-music-recovery | title = NPD: Dance games spark music recovery | first = Christopher | last = Dring | date = 2010-12-10 | accessdate = 2010-12-10 | publisher = [[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|MCV]] }}</ref>。[[彭博公司|彭博公司]]预计，Harmonix因销售《舞蹈中心》及其下载内容，2011年净利润将增长1亿美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-02/harmonix-rebounds-with-dance-central-bets-on-music-downloads.html | title = Harmonix Rebounds With Dance Central, Bets on Music Downloads | first = Alexandra | last = Dean | date= 2011-11-02 | accessdate= 2011-11-02 | publisher = [[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg L.P.]] }}</ref>。《舞力全开》尽管评价不佳，却击败《[[使命召唤：现代战争2|使命召唤：现代战争2]]》占据销量榜榜首<ref>Steinberg, p. 37</ref>，《[[舞力全开2|舞力全开2]]》（2010）是Wii上最畅销的非[[任天堂|任天堂]]游戏。[[舞力全开系列|舞力全开系列]]可与最畅销的动作游戏系列抗衡销量<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2011/07/14/just-dance-2-breaks-records-as-best-selling-third-party-wii-game.aspx | title = Just Dance 2 Breaks Records As Best-Selling Third-Party Wii Game | first = Matt | last = Helgeson | date = 2011-07-14 | accessdate = 2010-12-10 | publisher = ''[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]'' }}</ref>。Tap Tap是首款[[iPhone|iPhone]]节奏游戏系列，其首作《[[Tap_Tap_Revenge|Tap Tap Revenge]]》为该平台2008下载最多的游戏<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.businessinsider.com/tap-tap-revenge-2-already-top-iphone-app-nearing-500000-downloads-2009-3 | title = 'Tap Tap Revenge 2' Already Top iPhone App, 500,000 Downloads | first = Dan | last = Frommer | date = 2009-03-05 | accessdate = 2011-10-13 | publisher = [[Business_Insider|Business Insider]] }}</ref>。Tap Tap系列最终以1500万的下载量，获得[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]之“最受欢迎iPhone游戏系列”认证<ref>{{cite web | url = http://news.cnet.com/8301-27076_3-20062715-248.html | title = iPhone 4, App Store nab Guinness World Records | first = Josh | last = Lowensohn | date = 2011-05-13 | accessdate = 2011-10-13 | publisher = [[CNET|CNET]] }}</ref>。

在2014年中，随着[[独立游戏|独立游戏]]现象，节奏游戏有了一些变化<ref>{{cite web | url = http://pixelkin.org/2014/10/29/favorite-rhythm-games/ | title = 5 RHYTHM AND MUSIC GAMES YOU SHOULD DEFINITELY TRY | first = Simone| last = deRochefort| date = 2014-10-29 | accessdate = 2015-01-08 | publisher = ''Pixelkin'' }}</ref>。在《[[丛林群殴|丛林群殴]]》中，玩家要连续点击触摸屏操作游戏，不同的节奏代表不同的动作，玩家以此方式环境中的角色。而在《[[节奏地牢|节奏地牢]]》，玩家要按背景音乐的节拍来控制主角。

== 健康与教育 ==

节奏游戏已用来健身。例如研究发现，相较传统游戏，舞蹈游戏可大量消耗能量，其燃烧热量超过在跑步机上走步。科学家还提出，因儿童长时间玩游戏看电视，可以活动身体的游戏防治[[肥胖|肥胖]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/content/124/2/534.full | publisher = ''[[Pediatrics_(journal)|Pediatrics]]'' | date =2009-07-13 | accessdate = 2011-11-14 | title = Playing Active Video Games Increases Energy Expenditure in Children | last = Graf, Diana L.; Pratt, Lauren V.; Hester, Casey N.; Short, Kevin R.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2007/01/070104144703.htm | publisher = [[Science_Daily|Science Daily]] | date =2007-01-04 | accessdate = 2011-11-12 | title = Adding Activity To Video Games Fights Obesity, Study Shows | last = [[Mayo_Clinic|Mayo Clinic]] }}</ref>。研究发现，按有效[[心率|心率]]而非[[最大摄氧量|最大摄氧量]]下限计，游玩《舞蹈革命》相当于[[有氧运动|有氧运动]]<ref name="Unnithan">{{Cite journal| doi = 10.1055/s-2005-872964 | pmid = 17006803 | publisher = ''[[International_Journal_of_Sports_Medicine|International Journal of Sports Medicine]]'' | date =October 2006 | title = Evaluation of the energy cost of playing a dance simulation video game in overweight and non-overweight children and adolescents | journal = International Journal of Sports Medicine | volume = 27 | issue = 10 | pages = 804–9 | last = Unnithan, V.B.; Houser, W.; Fernhall B.| first1 = V. | last2 = Houser | first2 = W. | last3 = Fernhall | first3 = B. }}</ref><ref name="lieberman">{{cite web|url=http://www.comm.ucsb.edu/faculty/lieberman/exergames.htm |publisher=[[University_of_California,_Santa_Barbara|University of California, Santa Barbara]] |date=2006-04-15 |accessdate=2011-11-15 |title=Dance Games and Other Exergames: What the Research Says |last=Lieberman |first=Debra A. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103034538/http://www.comm.ucsb.edu/faculty/lieberman/exergames.htm |archivedate=2011-11-03 }}</ref>。西弗吉尼亚州是美国肥胖及并发疾病者比率最高的州之一，该州按成功的初步研究，向学校体育课引入《舞蹈革命》游戏<ref name="lieberman" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/2100-204_162-685644.html?tag=contentMain;contentBody | publisher = ''[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]'' | date =2009-02-11 | accessdate = 2011-11-15 | title = Dancing The Pounds Away | first = Allison | last = Barker }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》称，“至少十州的数百所学校”在课程中用到《舞蹈革命》（以及《[[In_the_Groove|In the Groove]]》）<ref name="lieberman" />。为减轻国民肥胖蔓延的问题，该计划将应用于千余所学校<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/04/30/health/30exer.html | publisher = ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' | date =2007-04-30 | accessdate = 2011-11-12 | title = P.E. Classes Turn to Video Game That Works Legs | first = Seth | last = Schiesel }}</ref>。原加利福尼亚州长[[阿诺德·施瓦辛格|阿诺德·施瓦辛格]]是此类计划的著名支持者<ref name="ashcraft65">Ashcraft, p. 65</ref>。日本有报道明星玩《舞蹈革命》后减重，这促进了游戏家用机版本的销售。Bemani测试员也发现，他们工作中减轻了体重<ref name="ashcraft65" />。虽然还有轶事证明游戏有助减肥<ref name="lieberman" />，但密歇根健康系统大学谨慎表示，舞蹈和其他运动游戏只是和起点，之后应转向更有效的传统运动<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.med.umich.edu/opm/newspage/2008/hmvideogames.htm |publisher=[[University_of_Michigan_Health_System|University of Michigan Health System]] |date=2008-03-03 |accessdate=2011-11-15 |title=Video games and exercise: High-energy games get kids off the couch, but shouldn't replace real sports |first=Katie |last=Vloet |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110921204359/http://www.med.umich.edu/opm/newspage/2008/hmvideogames.htm |archivedate=2011-09-21 }}</ref>。舞蹈游戏还用于老年患者康复与防跌计划表，但游戏为定制的慢版，同时还加配防护垫<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.brw.com.au/p/sections/health/computer_games_keep_elderly_on_their_68lVidRD8BNWwZtOzxzhzM | publisher = ''[[Business_Review_Weekly|Business Review Weekly]]'' | date = 2011-07-21 | accessdate = 2011-11-14 | title = Computer Games Keep Elderly on Their Toes | first = Jeanne-Vida | last = Douglas | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111014024601/http://brw.com.au/p/sections/health/computer_games_keep_elderly_on_their_68lVidRD8BNWwZtOzxzhzM | archive-date = 2011-10-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。研究人员为获得普遍而逼真的步伐，还试验了原形游戏，而非止于商业舞蹈游戏筛选的动作<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.icdvrat.reading.ac.uk/2010/papers/ICDVRAT2010_S08_N01_Lange_etal.pdf | publisher = [[University_of_Southern_California|University of Southern California]] | date =2010-08-31 | accessdate = 2011-11-14 | title = Development of an interactive stepping game to reduce falls in the elderly | last = Lange; Flynn; Chang; Liang; Chieng; Rizzo}}</ref>。

吉他英雄游戏因需多肢体协调，故随同物理疗法，用于中风康复治疗<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2008/sep/24/you-dont-have-to-be-a-quick-fingered-15-year-old-t/ | title= Healing with Guitar Hero | publisher = ''[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]'' | date = 2008-09-24 | accessdate = 2011-11-12 | first = Gabriella | last = Boston}}</ref>。[[金髮美女|金髮美女]]鼓手克雷姆·伯克与[[奇切斯特大学|奇切斯特大学]]和[[格鲁斯特大学|格鲁斯特大学]]的研究者合作得出结论，吉他英雄类游戏可以解决“儿童与成人肥胖、孤独症、脑卒中、工作场所身心健康”的问题<ref name="sun">{{cite news | url = http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/woman/health/article2212761.ece | title = Beat it for a better brain | work = [[The_Sun_(newspaper)|The Sun]] | first = Andrea | last = Hammett | date = 2009-02-06 | accessdate = 2011-11-12}}</ref>。[[约翰斯霍普金斯大学|约翰斯霍普金斯大学]]的研究者用《吉他英雄III》和控制器，帮助了截肢患者，并为其开发了新型假肢<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.jhu.edu/~gazette/2009/23feb09/23guitar.html | title = Guitar Heroes: APL Riff on Video Game Helps Prosthetic Patients | first = Paulette | last = Campbell | date = 2009-02-23 | accessdate = 2009-11-12 | publisher = The JHU Gazette}}</ref>。[[内华达大学里诺校区|内华达大学里诺校区]]研究者为《[[热火吉他手|热火吉他手]]》——仿制吉他英雄的免费软件——定制触觉反馈手套，制作了音乐游戏《盲人英雄》，视觉障碍者可仅借触觉和听觉游玩<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5092565/frets-on-fire-for-the-blind | title = Frets On Fire For The Blind | first = Stuart | last = Houghton | date = 2008-11-19 | accessdate = 2011-11-12 | publisher = Kotaku}}</ref>。麻省理工大学学生、新加坡政府，和一名[[新加坡国立大学|新加坡国立大学]]合作，制作了同讓盲人和健康玩家游玩的《音频奥德赛》<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/04/education/edlife/ideas-blindvideo-t.html?_r=2 | title = See Me, Hear Me: A Video Game for the Blind | first = Abby | last = Ellin | date = 2008-12-26 | accessdate = 2011-11-14 | publisher = ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''}}</ref>。[[特伦特大学|特伦特大学]]还在青少年睡眠研究中用到吉他英雄，研究显示，同为12小时后重玩歌曲，一般情况下之间若有正常睡眠，再度演奏效果会更好<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vancouversun.com/life/Motor+skills+rest+sleep+levels+Study/3446033/story.html | title = Motor skills rest on sleep levels: Study | first = Misty | last = Harris | date = 2010-08-26 | accessdate = 2011-11-12 | work = [[Vancouver_Sun|Vancouver Sun]] }}</ref>。

吉他英雄和摇滚乐队向人们介绍了摇滚乐，他们也因此学习吉他演奏。青年音乐的研究表明，在英国1,200万儿童中，有250万是玩过吉他英雄等音乐游戏后，开始学习真实乐器。组织认为这些游戏可纳入音乐教育计划<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/features/can-gaming-save-the-record-industry-1192251.html | title = Can gaming save the record industry? | publisher = ''[[The_Independent|The Independent]]'' | date = 2008-12-17 | accessdate = 2011-11-11}}</ref>。美国吉他教师称，吉他学生因吉他英雄游戏而增长。然而业界专家，如练习工具[[Fretlight|Fretlight]]发明者表示，怀疑游戏的教育价值。虽有轶闻证明，吉他英雄能提升节奏感、训练手的总体协调性，但却让学生错误认识学习难度，以至放弃学习<ref name="salon guitar hero">{{cite web|url=http://machinist.salon.com/feature/2007/08/15/guitar_hero/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080811141022/http://machinist.salon.com/feature/2007/08/15/guitar_hero/ |archivedate=2008-08-11 |title=How "Guitar Hero" saved guitar music |first=Farhad |last=Manjoo |publisher=[[Salon.com|Salon.com]] |date=2007-08-15 |accessdate=2011-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。吉他中心的调查发现，大多数乐器式节奏游戏玩家，将来有意拿起真正的乐器，而大多已是乐手的玩家，希望继续演奏自己的乐器<ref name="nebula" />。吉他虽然如此流行，却未达1960年代的程度<ref name="salon guitar hero" />。一些音乐家批评吉他英雄对音乐教育的影响。[[白線條樂團|白線條樂團]]的[[杰克·怀特|杰克·怀特]]称，在听到年轻人最可能由电子游戏接触新作品后，他感到了失望，[[齐柏林飞船_(乐团)|齐柏林飞船]]的[[吉米·佩奇|吉米·佩奇]]表示，他无法相信人能从电子游戏仿制品中，学到如何演奏真乐器<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nme.com/news/the-white-stripes/45521 | title = Jack White and Jimmy Page diss 'Guitar Hero' video game | publisher = [[NME|NME]] | date = 2009-06-22 | accessdate = 2009-06-23 }}</ref>。[[王子_(音樂家)|普林斯]]推掉了自己音乐在吉他英雄登场的机会，他称“孩子学到如何弹真吉他更为重要”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pbs.org/kcet/tavissmiley/archive/200904/20090428_prince.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5hO40dHzy?url=http://www.pbs.org/kcet/tavissmiley/archive/200904/20090428_prince.html |archivedate=2009-06-08 |publisher=[[Public_Broadcasting_Service|PBS]] |date=2009-04-28 |accessdate=2009-04-30 |title=Prince |first=Tavis |last=Smiley |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。其他评论称，鼓控制器有潜在教育效果，或能让玩家用真鼓创作音乐<ref name="sun" /><ref name="nebula">{{cite web | url = http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_6986/is_3_6/ai_n54399025/ | title = Guitar Hero world tour: a creator of new sonic experiences? | first = Matthew | last = Ingram | publisher = ''[[Nebula|Nebula]]'' | date = September 2009 | accessdate = 2011-11-16 }}</ref>。

